        "content": "# Data availability\n\nThis dashboard relies on optional network metrics.\nNetwork metrics can be enable on a per cluster basis, see our tutorial at https://docs.giantswarm.io/tutorials/observability/network-monitoring/. Please contact team Atlas for more information.\n\n# Information\n\nThis dashboard only visualizes data for network traffic coming from a identified namespace(s) (usually Pods) over a long period of time. Traffic outside namespace is ignored (e.g. Node, AWS resolver, load balancer). For a detailed view use the **Network Traffic Analysis** dashboard. ",
